queries.sql: SELECT `transactions`.*, `properties`.`title` as `property_title`, `properties`.`reference` as `property_ref`, CONCAT(client.first_name, " ", client.last_name) as client_name, CONCAT(agent.first_name, " ", agent.last_name) as agent_name FROM `transactions` LEFT JOIN `properties` ON `properties`.`id` = `transactions`.`property_id` LEFT JOIN `clients` as `client` ON `client`.`id` = `transactions`.`client_id` LEFT JOIN `users` as `agent` ON `agent`.`id` = `transactions`.`agent_id` WHERE `transactions`.`agency_id` = '12' ORDER BY `transactions`.`created_at` DESC
